{"about_the_game":"Get ready to face countless waves of relentless enemies <br>with powerful weapons and strategically placed turrets at your disposal<br>whether you're flying solo or teaming up with friends in co-op mode<br>So jump in, gear up, and let the mayhem begin!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Base.png?t=1726499305\" /><br>Defend your base against incoming threats by using your weapons and building defenses.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Gif_BaseDefend.gif?t=1726499305\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Defense.png?t=1726499305\" /><br>Need more firepower? Okay.<br>Set up a defense turret and slow down those enemies <br>with barricades and other sweet obstacles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Gif_Building.gif?t=1726499305\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Solo-Coop.png?t=1726499305\" /><br>Hey, look! your friends are here!<br>play with your friends up to 24 players<br>brainstorm plans, ideas, skills, and firepower<br>to stop the enemies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Gif_Co-Op.gif?t=1726499305\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Horde.png?t=1726499305\" /><br>take on a never-ending wave of enemies<br>that randomly generates each run you play. <br>fight until the game crashes and let's see how long you can last!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972530/extras/Gif_Horde.gif?t=1726499305\" /><br><b